    "groupId": "scenario-12-15",
    "scenarioTitle": "材料题 12-15",
    "scenario": "SCENARIO(12-15)\nYou have just been hired by a toy manufacturer based in Hong Kong. The company sells a broad range of dolls, action figures and plush toys that can be found internationally in a wide variety of retail stores. Although the manufacturer has no offices outside Hong Kong and in fact does not employ any staff outside Hong Kong, it has entered into a number of local distribution contracts. The toys produced by the company can be found in all popular toy stores throughout Europe, the United States and Asia. A large portion of the company's revenue is due to international sales.\n场景题（12-15题）\n你刚刚受雇于一家总部位于香港的玩具制造商。该公司销售种类繁多的玩偶、动作人偶和毛绒玩具，产品通过全球各地的零售商店销往国际市场。尽管该制造商在香港以外没有任何办事处，实际上也未在香港以外雇佣任何员工，但已签订了多项本地分销合同。该公司生产的玩具可在欧洲、美国和亚洲的所有热门玩具店购买，国际销售额占公司总收入的很大一部分。\nGDPR第3条territorial scope：offering of the services or goods 或者是monitoring of their behaviours.\nThe company now wishes to launch a new range of connected toys, ones that can talk and interact with children. The CEO of the company is touting these toys as the next big thing, due to the increased possibilities offered: The figures can answer children's questions on various subjects, such as mathematical calculations or the weather. Each figure is equipped with a microphone and speaker and can connect to any smartphone or tablet via Bluetooth. Any mobile device within a 10-meter radius can connect to the toys via Bluetooth as well. The figures can also be associated with other figures (from the same manufacturer) and interact with each other for an enhanced play experience. When a child asks the toy a question, the request is sent to the cloud for analysis, and the answer is generated on cloud servers and sent back to the figure. The answer is given through the figure's integrated speakers, making it appear as though that the toy is actually responding to the child's question. The packaging of the toy does not provide technical details on how this works, nor does it mention that this feature requires an internet connection. (本质上是对数据主体的知情权造成了损害) The necessary data processing for this has been outsourced to a data center located in South Africa. However, your company has not yet revised its consumer-facing privacy policy to indicate this.（本质上是对数据主体的知情权造成了损害，因为没有告知数据主体处理者是谁，也没告诉数据主体是如何运作的）\n该公司现在计划推出一系列新型智能玩具，这些玩具能够与儿童对话和互动。公司首席执行官称这些玩具将成为下一个热门产品，因为其具备更多功能：这些人偶可以回答儿童关于各种主题的问题，如数学计算或天气情况。每个人偶均配备麦克风和扬声器，可通过蓝牙连接至任何智能手机或平板电脑。任何位于 10 米范围内的移动设备也可通过蓝牙连接至这些玩具。这些人偶还可与其他（同一制造商生产的）人偶关联，并相互互动以提升游戏体验。当儿童向玩具提问时，请求会发送至云端进行分析，答案在云服务器上生成后发送回人偶，并通过人偶的内置扬声器播放，使人感觉玩具正在直接回应儿童的问题。玩具包装上未提供相关技术细节说明其工作原理，也未提及此功能需要互联网连接。相关数据处理工作已外包给位于南非的数据中心，但贵公司尚未修订面向消费者的隐私政策以说明这一情况。\nIn parallel, the company is planning to introduce a new range of game systems through which consumers can play the characters they acquire in the course of playing the game. The system will come bundled with a portal that includes a Near-Field Communications (NFC) reader. This device will read an RFID tag in the action figure, making the figure come to life onscreen. Each character has  its  own  stock  features and abilities, but it is also possible  to  earn additional ones by accomplishing game goals. The only information stored in the tag relates to the figures 'abilities.It is easy to switch characters during the game, and it is possible to bring the figure to locations outside of the home and have the character's abilities remain intact.\n同时，该公司计划推出一系列新的游戏系统，消费者可通过该系统操控在游戏过程中获得的角色。该系统将附带一个包含近场通信（NFC）读取器的端口设备，该设备可读取动作人偶中的射频识别（RFID）标签，使人偶在屏幕上 “活起来”。每个角色都有其自身的固有特征和技能，但也可通过完成游戏目标获得额外技能。标签中仅存储与人偶技能相关的信息。游戏过程中可轻松切换角色，且可将人偶带离家庭环境，其角色技能仍保持不变。"
