    "scenario": "SCENARIO(36-40)\nLiem, an online retailer known for its environmentally friendly shoes, has recently expanded its presence in Europe. Anxious to achieve market dominance, Liem teamed up with another eco-friendly company, EcoMick, which sells accessories like belts and bags. Together the companies drew up a series of marketing campaigns designed to highlight the environmental and economic benefits of their products. After months of planning, Liem and EcoMick entered into a data sharing agreement to use the same marketing database, MarketIQ, to send the campaigns to their respective contacts.\nLiem and EcoMick also entered into a data processing agreement with MarketIQ, the terms of which included processing personal data only upon Liem and EcoMick's instructions, and making available to them all information necessary to demonstrate compliance with GDPR obligations.\n场景题（36-40题）\n利姆公司（Liem）是一家以环保鞋履闻名的网上零售商，最近已扩大其在欧洲的业务。为急于实现市场主导地位，利姆公司与另一家环保公司 —— 生态米克公司（EcoMick）合作，该公司销售腰带和包袋等配饰。两家公司共同制定了一系列营销活动，旨在突出其产品的环境和经济效益。经过数月的规划，利姆公司和生态米克公司签订了数据共享协议，使用同一个营销数据库 “市场智汇”（MarketIQ）向各自的联系人发送营销活动信息。\n利姆公司和生态米克公司还与 “市场智汇”（MarketIQ）签订了数据处理协议，协议条款包括仅根据利姆公司和生态米克公司的指示处理个人数据，并向其提供证明符合GDPR义务所需的所有信息。\nLiem and EcoMick then procured the services of a company called JaphSoft, a marketing optimization firm that uses machine learning to help companies run successful campaigns. Clients provide JaphSoft with the personal data of individuals they would like to be targeted in each campaign. To ensure protection of its clients' data, JaphSoft（处理者）implements the technical and organizational measures it deems appropriate. JaphSoft works to continually improve its machine learning models by analyzing the data it receives from its clients to determine the most successful components of a successful campaign. JaphSoft then uses such models in providing services to its client-base. Since the models improve only over a period of time as more information is collected, JaphSoft does not have a deletion process for the data it receives from clients. However, to ensure compliance with data privacy rules, JaphSoft pseudonymizes the personal data by removing identifying information from the contact information. JaphSoft's engineers, however, maintain all contact information in the same database as the identifying information.\n随后，利姆公司和生态米克公司聘请了一家名为杰普软件公司（JaphSoft）的营销优化公司，该公司利用机器学习帮助企业开展成功的营销活动。客户向杰普软件公司提供其希望在每次活动中作为目标对象的个人数据。为确保保护客户数据，杰普软件公司实施了其认为适当的技术和组织措施。杰普软件公司通过分析从客户那里收到的数据，确定成功营销活动的最有效组成部分，不断改进其机器学习模型。然后，杰普软件公司利用这些模型为其客户群提供服务。由于模型只有在收集更多信息后经过一段时间才能改进，杰普软件公司对其从客户那里收到的数据没有删除程序。不过，为确保符合数据隐私规则，杰普软件公司通过从联系信息中删除识别信息来对个人数据进行假名化处理。但杰普软件公司的工程师将所有联系信息与识别信息存储在同一个数据库中。\nUnder its agreement with Liem and EcoMick, JaphSoft received access to MarketIQ, which included contact information as well as prior purchase history for such contacts, to create campaigns that would result in the most views of the two companies' websites. A prior Liem customer, Ms. Iman, received a marketing campaign from JaphSoft regarding Liem's as well as EcoMick's latest products. While Ms. Iman recalls checking a box to receive information in the future regarding Liem's products, she has never shopped EcoMick, nor provided her personal data to that company.\n根据其与利姆公司和生态米克公司的协议，杰普软件公司获得了 “市场智汇”（MarketIQ）的访问权限，其中包括联系人信息以及这些联系人的过往购买记录，以创建能使两家公司网站获得最多浏览量的营销活动。利姆公司的一位老客户——伊曼女士（Ms. Iman）收到了杰普软件公司关于利姆公司和生态米克公司最新产品的营销活动信息。伊曼女士记得曾勾选过一个方框，同意未来接收利姆公司产品的相关信息，但她从未在生态米克公司购物，也未向该公司提供过其个人数据。"
