    "prompt": "If a company is planning to use closed-circuit television (CCTV) on its premises and is concerned with GDPR compliance, it should first do all of the following EXCEPT?\n如果一家公司计划在其场所安装闭路电视（CCTV），并关注GDPR合规性，它应首先采取以下所有措施，除了？",
