    "scenario": "SCENARIO(67-70)\nT-Craze, a German-headquartered specialty t-shirt company, was successfully selling to large German metropolitan cities. However, after a recent merger with another German-based company that was selling to a broader European market, T-Craze revamped its marketing efforts to sell to a wider audience. These efforts included a complete design of its logo to reflect the recent merger, and improvements to its website meant to capture more information about visitors through the use of cookies.\n场景题（67-70题）\nT-Craze是一家总部位于德国的专业T恤公司，此前成功面向德国各大城市销售产品。然而，在与另一家面向更广泛欧洲市场的德国公司合并后，T-Craze重新调整了营销策略，以拓展更广泛的客户群体。这些举措包括重新设计标志以反映此次合并，并改进其网站，通过使用Cookie收集更多访问者信息。\nT-Craze also opened various office locations throughout Europe to help expand its business. While Germany continued to host T-Craze's headquarters and main product-design office, its French affiliate became responsible for all marketing and sales activities. The French affiliate recently procured the services of Right Target, a renowned marketing firm based in the Philippines, to run its latest marketing campaign. After thorough research, Right Target determined that T-Craze is most successful with customers between the ages of 18 and 22. Thus, its first campaign target university students in several European capitals, which yielded nearly 40% new customers for T-Craze in one quarter. Right Target also ran subsequent campaigns for T-Craze, though with much less success.\nT-Craze 还在欧洲各地开设了多个办事处以助力业务扩张。尽管德国仍设有T-Craze的总部和主要产品设计办公室，但其法国关联公司负责所有营销和销售活动。该法国关联公司最近聘请了菲律宾知名营销公司Right Target（精准目标公司）负责其最新营销活动。经过深入研究，Right Target确定T-Craze在18至22岁客户群体中最受欢迎。因此，其首个营销活动以多个欧洲首都的大学生为目标，在一个季度内为T-Craze带来了近40%的新客户。Right Target随后还为T-Craze开展了多次营销活动，但成效远不如前。\nThe last two campaigns included a wider demographic group and resulted in countless unsubscribe requests, including a large number in Spain. In fact, the Spanish data protection authority received a complaint from Sofia, amid-career investment banker. Sofia was upset after receiving a marketing communication even after unsubscribing from such communications from the Right Target on behalf of T-Craze.\n最后两次活动覆盖了更广泛的人口统计群体，导致无数退订请求，其中西班牙的退订量尤为庞大。事实上，西班牙数据保护机构收到了索菲亚（Sofia）的投诉，她是一名处于职业生涯中期的投资银行家。索菲亚在退订了Right Target代表T-Craze发送的营销信息后，仍收到相关营销沟通，对此感到不满。"
