    "explanation": "这是技术问题不是法律问题，不能因为自己技术不行就不承担责任。（只要记住这句就好理解，想要仔细探究的再看下面）\n见Guidelines 01/2022 on data subject rights - Right of access（访问权）。\n选项A，Para 55，However, if the data subject sends a request to the controller’s employee who has been assigned to them as their regular contact person (such as e.g. a personal account manager at a bank or a regular consultant at a mobile phone operator), such contact should not to be considered as a random one and the controller should make all reasonable efforts, to handle such a request so that it can be redirected to the contact point and answered within the time limits provided for by the GDPR. 第55段，然而，若数据主体将请求发送给已被指定为其常规联系人的控制者员工（例如银行的个人客户经理或移动运营商的专属顾问），该联系人不应被视为随机接收请求的人员，控制者应尽一切合理努力处理该请求，确保其被转交给指定联络点，并在GDPR规定的时限内予以答复。\n选项B，Para 60，Art. 12(2) GDPR states that the controller shall not refuse to act on the request of the data subject to exercise his or her rights, unless the controller processes personal data for a purpose that does not require the identification of the data subject and it demonstrates that it is not in a position to identify the data subject. In such circumstances, the data subject may, however, decide to provide additional information enabling this identification (Art. 11(2) GDPR). 第60段， GDPR第12条第2款规定，控制者不得拒绝响应数据主体行使其权利的请求，除非控制者处理个人数据的目的无需识别数据主体，且能证明无法识别该数据主体。但在此情况下，数据主体可选择提供有助于识别身份的补充信息（GDPR第11条第2款）。\n选项C，Para 40，In cases where data security requirements would necessitate end-to-end encryption of electronic mails but the controller would only be able to send a normal e-mail, the controller will have to use other means, such as sending a USB-stick by (registered) letter post to the data subject. 第40段，若数据安全要求电子邮件必须采用端到端加密，但控制者仅能发送普通电子邮件，则控制者必须采用其他方式向数据主体提供相关信息，如通过挂号信寄送 U 盘。\n选项D，Para 37，Controllers are thus not required to provide personal data, which they processed in the past but which they no longer have at their disposal. 第37段，因此，对于控制者过去曾处理但现已不再持有的个人数据，控制者无需向数据主体提供。\nSCENARIO-(270-274)\nGentle Hedgehog Inc. is a privately owned website design agency incorporated in Italy. The company has numerous remote workers in different EU countries. Recently, the management of Gentle Hedgehog noticed a decrease in productivity of their sales team, especially among remote workers. As a result, the company plans to implement a robust but privacy-friendly remote surveillance system to prevent absenteeism, reward top performers, and ensure the best quality of customer service when salespeople are interacting with customers.\n场景题（270-274题）\n刺猬绅士公司（Gentle Hedgehog Inc.）是一家在意大利注册的私营网站设计机构，在欧盟多个国家拥有众多远程员工。最近，刺猬绅士公司的管理层注意到其销售团队的生产力下降，尤其是远程员工。因此，公司计划实施一套强大但符合隐私保护要求的远程监控系统，以防止旷工、奖励表现优秀的员工，并确保销售人员与客户互动时提供最优质的客户服务。\nGentle Hedgehog eventually hires Sauron Eye Inc., a Chinese vendor of employee surveillance software whose European headquarters is in Germany. Sauron Eye’s software provides powerful remote-monitoring capabilities, including 24/7 access to computer cameras and microphones, screen captures, emails, website history, and keystrokes. Any device can be remotely monitored from a central server that is securely installed at Gentle Hedgehog headquarters. The monitoring is invisible by default; however, a so-called Transparent Mode, which regularly and conspicuously notifies all users about the monitoring and its precise scope, also exists. Additionally, the monitored employees are required to use a built-in verification technology involving facial recognition each time they log in.\nAll monitoring data, including the facial recognition data, is securely stored in Microsoft Azure cloud servers operated by Sauron Eye, which are physically located in France.\n刺猬绅士公司最终聘请了索伦之眼公司（Sauron Eye Inc.）—— 一家总部位于德国的中国员工监控软件供应商。索伦之眼公司的软件提供强大的远程监控功能，包括全天候访问电脑摄像头和麦克风、屏幕截图、电子邮件、网站浏览历史和按键记录。任何设备均可通过安装在刺猬绅士公司总部的安全中央服务器进行远程监控。该监控默认处于隐藏模式；不过，该软件还设有所谓的 “透明模式”，会定期且显著地通知所有用户监控事宜及其确切范围。此外，被监控员工每次登录时均需使用内置的面部识别验证技术。所有监控数据（包括面部识别数据）均安全存储在索伦之眼公司运营的微软Azure云服务器上，该服务器物理位于法国。",
